# AI Integration

The application integrates with AI capabilities through custom modules.

## AI Modules
- Uses @defikitdotnet/education-module-ai for educational content
- Uses @defikitdotnet/public-agent-module for public AI agents
- Uses @defikitdotnet/x-ai-combat for AI competition features

## Agent Management
- Provides interfaces for creating and configuring AI agents
- Enables training and fine-tuning of AI models
- Supports agent interaction and debugging

## Educational Content
- AI-powered educational modules
- Interactive learning experiences
- Progress tracking and assessment

## API Integration
- Connects to external AI services and APIs
- Implements rate limiting and request caching
- Handles streaming responses for real-time AI interactions
